yubico-piv-tool
------------------------------------------
The Yubico PIV tool is used for interacting with the Privilege and
Identification Card (PIV) application on a YubiKey.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libpcsclite1-2.2.3-1bl1
  libssl-devel-3.0.14-1
  libssl3-3.0.14-1
  libykpiv-devel-2.6.0-1bl1
  libykpiv2-2.6.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1
  zlib0-1.3.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gengetopt-2.23-1
  help2man-1.49.3-1
  libpcsclite-devel-2.2.3-1bl1
  libssl-devel-3.0.14-1
  ninja-1.12.0-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/Yubico/yubico-piv-tool

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/Yubico/yubico-piv-tool/archive/refs/tags/yubico-piv-tool-2.6.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack yubico-piv-tool-2.6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./yubico-piv-tool-2.6.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/yubico-piv-tool-2.6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/yubico-piv-tool-2.6.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libykpiv2-2.6.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libykpiv-devel-2.6.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(yubico-piv-tool)
  /usr/bin/yubico-piv-tool.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/yubico-piv-tool.README
  /usr/share/doc/yubico-piv-tool/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/yubico-piv-tool/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/yubico-piv-tool/README
  /usr/share/man/man1/yubico-piv-tool.1.gz

(libykpiv2)
  /usr/bin/cygykcs11-2.dll
  /usr/bin/cygykpiv-2.dll

(libykpiv-devel)
  /usr/include/ykpiv/ykpiv-config.h
  /usr/include/ykpiv/ykpiv.h
  /usr/lib/libykcs11.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libykpiv.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/ykcs11.pc
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/ykpiv.pc

